Original Issue: Describe the bug
Native Postman app cookies are not being updated when they change in Chrome (using Interceptor extension for Chrome)
To Reproduce
Steps to reproduce the behavior:

Turn on interceptor and add localhost as a domain to track cookies for
Log in to web app on localhost in Chrome
Check that cookie has been tracked by Interceptor in Postman app
Log out of web app on localhost in Chrome
Log in to web app on localhost in Chrome
Cookie value has not been updated in Postman app, regardless of the fact that it has changed in Chrome

Expected behavior
According to the docs, Postman and Interceptor should keep the cookies in sync for the selected domains between Chrome and Postman.

Interceptor keeps cookies for a fixed set of domains in sync, updating Postman from the browser when cookies update, including deletions.
